Package: netReg
Type: Package
Title: Network-regularized regression models
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-05-15
Authors@R: person("Simon", "Dirmeier", email = "simon.dirmeier@gmx.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Simon Dirmeier, <simon.dirmeier@gmx.de>
Description: netReg fits linear models using network-regularized regression.
    Graph prior knowledge is incorporated into the objective function of the linear
    model in the form of affinity matrices.
